# CODEOWNERS
# Defines who gets automatically requested as a reviewer for each path.
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default: every PR requires at least one reviewer from the team
*                           @your-org/expense-tracker-reviewers

# Database schema changes require extra scrutiny
db/schema.cds               @your-org/db-owners
db/data/                    @your-org/db-owners

# Service layer
srv/                        @your-org/backend-owners

# CI/CD pipeline changes
.github/                    @your-org/devops-team
